#: includes/Gateway.php:19
msgid "Accept USDT and USDC at checkout. Settled on-chain in the same stablecoin, no chargebacks."
msgstr "Приём USDT и USDC на оформлении заказа. Расчёт on-chain в том же стейблкоине, без чарджбэков."

#: includes/Gateway.php:30 includes/Gateway.php:49 includes/Blocks.php:51
